data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming side hall colonial boasts a welcoming entry sunroom leading into a spacious living room, formal dining room, well-appointed kitchen, and convenient full bath on the main floor. Upstairs, discover three inviting bedrooms alongside another full bath for added comfort. Need extra space? Ascend to the fully finished attic, perfect for a home office, game room etc. The partially finished basement offers endless possibilities for customization. Recent updates including a newer water heater, boiler, and roof, all completed within the last four years, ensure peace of mind. Situated in a sought-after location, just minutes from transportation, major highways, Branch Brook Park, and other amenities, this home truly offers the best of comfort, convenience, and modern living. LOW Taxes!
